content: SUGGESTION: You should add what will be the first day of the month. Everybody receives there salary on different days of the month, So it will be very helpful if you add this.
A great app indeed. It is the most useful app I have ever used in my whole life. Although, I don’t even know what it actually. I am rating this app, just because my friend made this.
Very Good App and user friendly. UI is good. Using the Pro version. I am enjoying using this App. Thanks to the developer ! Recommend to use this App.
It's good so far.

Simple and easy to use app. I prefer this app over budget apps that allow you to link your accounts. This budget app is more interactive in that you have to manually input your accounts, income, expenses etc. Because of that, the appmakes you look more at how you're spending, at least it does for me.
neat and simple, more nice icon please! and more customization pls
Good App, but some additional featured required like auto balance transfer from one month to another months.
Best I've ever used. I know where I am in my spending now. Love it.
I love it!
I love using this because its easy to use. Thank you

It's a good manual-entry personal finances app, but it can use some improvement: 1) more icons! LOTS more icons! 2) custom budget entries the user can choose due dates for, and 3) negative initial values (for credit cards — another user mentioned this). The premium version is very reasonably priced. And, THIS APP ISN'T MADE IN RED CHINA.
Easy to use.

Overall easy to use and nice app. A feature to add accounts with initial negative balance (Credit Cards) would have been a great addition. Hoping to see this app grow and compete with the likes of Mobills and other expense manager apps.
Very convenient and user-friendly app.
I have looked at them all.This one is the best.
This app is just wonderful. It's by far the best budget app I have ever used.
Great app to keep track of simple stuff! Migrating from free to paid version is simple as hell too. Only suggestion would be some more cleaner themes :)
A very simple and useful app. The pro version is very affordable. I'm looking forward for the additional features such as easy adding of recurring transactions and facilitating back-up to the cloud.
Absolutely love this app. So simple to use. Budgeting and managing your accounts are made easy. Entering transactions takes two seconds. Nice job

An amazing, user-friendly, surprisingly good tool for those in budgeting mode. It's also completely customizable. The only thing that I'd like from the App is the ability to connect my actual bank accounts & debit cards for even more ease of use & efficiency, as well as for complete accuracy while you're building your budget. I started out with the free version of the App, but after using it I fell in love & ended up purchasing this pro edition. Thanks MyMoney Pro for making budgeting easy!
It's easy to use and allows me to check my spend against budget
Very VERY nice app. If you can tell me how or update to give ability to set recurring transactions (income and expenses), you get 5 stars.

A Red Theme would be cool This app has a lot of potential and that is why I bought it and it seems like the developer will stay with it.....Hopefully and not abandon it like most do with these apps
